title: US women’s soccer to play Trinidad in Honolulu on Dec. 6
text:
Home » News » Sports » US women's soccer to… US women’s soccer to play Trinidad in Honolulu on Dec. 6 By The Associated Press October 15, 2015 7:40 pm 
CHICAGO (AP) — The U.S. women’s team will play Trinidad and Tobago in Honolulu on Dec. 6 in the first international match played by the Americans in Hawaii. 
The Americans also will play Trinidad and Tobago on Dec. 10 at a site to be announced, the U.S. Soccer Federation said Thursday. 
The tour ends against China at the Superdome in New Orleans on Dec. 16. 
Two other December matches remain to be scheduled. Topics:
